# CLAUDE.local.md Template

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` for local settings (gitignored).

## Local Environment

```bash
# Ollama host (if not default)
export OLLAMA_HOST="http://localhost:11434"

# Anthropic API key for Claude backend
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="sk-ant-..."

# Brave Search API key (for MCP server)
export BRAVE_API_KEY="..."
```

## Personal Preferences

Add your personal coding preferences here:

- Preferred test runner flags
- Custom aliases
- IDE-specific notes

## Local Paths

If you have local model paths or custom configurations:

```bash
# Example: Local model cache
export OLLAMA_MODELS="/path/to/models"
```
